attributes.Long form description: The student begins by disassembling the table, first with the first two screws of the furniture using his hands. Once the screws are remove, the student begins to disassemble the top part of the table and then disassembles the middle part of the table by removing the two screws that hold it in place and then leaves them stacked on the table. The student repeats once to remove the bottom part of the cabinet and then begins to remove the wheels from the cabinet and finally disassembles the pillars of the cabinet by removing the screws and then stacks everything on the table.
